channel.title: SydneyScape [OFFICIAL]
channel.description:
Ok i thought instead of my ex-admin Tyler who STOLE my source releasing my server, i might aswell release the fixed version as his is buggy and old. [b]I WILL NOT RELEASE MY CLIENT AS ITS THE ONLY THING I HAVE LEFT![/b] Im not putting any pictures or big info ATM because im so pissed off about this...
If you want to see what its like and test it out before you download, then jsut go play it... Most people have.
SOME server features include: -many fixed dupes -custom teleports and interfaces -custom pest control -great stability -2 connections per ip address -MANY custom items -exp rates changed for EVERY skill -new pk zones -fixed barrage -many new bosses added -about 4 new FULL dungeons created -new and exciting ways to get custom items -custom weapon specials (like TB, freeze, and disable prot items) -Stability updates from Gnarly such as grahams eventmanager, ect... -A fun pk island -No commands for normal players -great economy -economy reset file included (just in case) -new commands such as unjail givemod demod and a lot more :/ -completely re-coded all the old delta minigames, i hate keeping them the same (all original) -every delta training area was scrapped and changed to my own -my own godwars -hilts -fixed ranging (def bonus and prayer)
LINK: [url=http://uppit.com/N8SC0W]http://uppit.com/N8SC0W[/url]
A few old pics... Ill add more later. [img]http://img357.imageshack.us/img357/1852/124loloz0.jpg[/img] [img]http://img386.imageshack.us/img386/3852/compilationaq6.jpg[/img] [img]http://img116.imageshack.us/img116/5608/hailbitchkt2.jpg[/img] [img]http://img387.imageshack.us/img387/584/sydneyedvillevb2.jpg[/img] [img]http://img116.imageshack.us/img116/3842/sydneyfuckon0.jpg[/img] [img]http://img380.imageshack.us/img380/7485/sydneyhailpcvg9.jpg[/img] [img]http://img237.imageshack.us/img237/9784/sydneyheadmx8.jpg[/img] [img]http://img386.imageshack.us/img386/4585/vengeancepj7.jpg[/img]
Enjoy you stupid leechers. SwiftY
Credits: (dont talk to me about them ok?!) Delta - 20% for releasing the source Gnarly - 5% for making much needed stability updates Me - 75% for the rest of the work
